<Content>Reasonable, professionally run but yes, risk of bedbugs Excellent location, variety of rooms with and without bath, responsible management (a plastic bag of personal items I left was there for me when I came back), ample hotwater, storage room for luggage while you travel elsewhere--but yes, I brought bedbugs back to my house once after staying there and had one bite another time so will probably not go back.. The hotel does have a vacuum cleaner, ask to have the rug vacuumed if you are there in the morning when cleaing is done. Elevator to upper floors. . 
